subject: JUnit Test Result DTD?
msgSnippet: Hi, I was wondering if anyone knows where I can find the DTD for JUnit test results. I have results of my own tests that I want to represent in the JUnit test
messageBody:
Hi,

I was wondering if anyone knows where I can find the DTD for JUnit
test results. I have results of my own tests that I want to
represent in the JUnit test result format so that I can use
junitreport on them to convert them to HTML.

Thank you so much in advance,

F. Kolchina
